WEBVTT

00:00:00.363 --> 00:00:03.697
You are about to hear the sounds
of the largest-toothed predator

00:00:03.697 --> 00:00:04.963
on the planet:

00:00:04.997 --> 00:00:07.363
an animal bigger than a school bus

00:00:07.363 --> 00:00:10.430
with perhaps the most sophisticated
form of communication

00:00:10.463 --> 00:00:12.763
that has ever existed.

00:00:12.797 --> 00:00:18.797
(Video: whale clicking)